			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Ship score change is already done, though I doubt as you wanted it. Ships now give power based on total space. That alone hurts fluffing significantly. New max possible power for GBs is 5, minimum is 3. Max tech dooms will always be 770 now. Devices are now always considered level 5 regardless of their listed tech level.
<br />

<br />
It's already possible to have 100%+ survival rate on victory (adds 20% survival rate). Any more and you'll get rediculous survival rates that make it impossible to kill commies. Yes, it hurts to lose nice commies, I know damn well, but as is said, commies were born to die. :p
<br />

<br />
And as far as faster rebuilding, where were you when I was trying to get people to support someting similar? I've now given up on getting opinions from people on IRC in #archspace, people seem to forget they have a brain and voice. It's ironically only the top players that seem to add their opinions to any discussion, and it was them supporting such a change. Alot of players seem to assume that said players only want changes to benifit them, but ironically it's virtually always far from the case. It won't be done this set, that's for sure. There's plenty of interesting changes going into this next set though. They'll be posted later today.<br />_________________<br />TE, "Azg", Legion, TE, DF, LS/DSWL, Monkeys, MK, 21CN, NC</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
